modName: Main Theme Replacer - The Dragonborn Comes by Karliene
descriptionHtml:
This replaces the main skyrim theme in the main menu with Karliene's version of The Dragonborn Comes.
Simply Drag the Data folder into you Skyrim directory and you are done.
